      "rationale": "Not applicable at MRL 2 for this COU. Numerical solver error as a distinct factor from discretization error is required only at MRL 3 and above per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. The solver error contributions are bounded within the discretization error GCI reported under the Discretization Error factor, which is sufficient for MRL 2 decision-making. Separate iterative convergence error quantification beyond residual monitoring is not mandated at this risk level."
