      "rationale": "Not applicable at MRL 2 for this COU. Use error assessment (evaluating errors introduced by analyst setup choices beyond documented procedures) is required at MRL 3+ where model influence is High. At MRL 2 with Medium model influence, the SQA controls (version control, documented simulation protocol, and peer review of boundary condition setup) are sufficient to manage use error risk without a formal separate use error factor assessment."
