      "rationale": "Not applicable at MRL 2 for this COU. Formal model form uncertainty quantification (e.g., turbulence model sensitivity, constitutive law alternatives) is required at MRL 3+. At MRL 2, the selected k-omega SST turbulence model and power-law hemolysis damage model are consistent with published FDA pump simulation guidance and the validation evidence demonstrates adequate predictive accuracy for the COU QoI within the specified operating envelope."
